2003-06-08  Martin Baulig  <martin@ximian.com>

	* sources/debuggerwidgets/debuggersourceview.[ch]: New widget.
	Derives from GtkSourceView, but has a `debugger_populate_popup'
	signal which contains the coordinates where the menu popped up.

	* mono.debugger.gui/Makefile.am: Renamed debugger-widgets.dll ->
	mono.debugger.gui-sharp.dll.  This is required since gtk-sharp's
	signal emission code expects this name.

2003-06-08  Martin Baulig  <martin@ximian.com>

	* sources/gtksourceview/gtksourceview.c
	(gtk_source_view_add_pixbuf): g_strdup() the `key' since it's
	automatically freed by Mono's P/Invoke marshaller.

2003-01-18  Martin Baulig  <martin@ximian.com>

	* sources/gtksourceview/gtksourcebuffer.h
	(gtk_source_buffer_get_tag_end): Removed external declaration
	because this function does not exist.

2002-10-05  Martin Baulig  <martin@gnome.org>

	* generator/gtk-api.xml (gtk_source_view_remove_all_markers):
	Removed this for the moment, it exists in the header file, but
	there is no implementation.

